It was the first time I’d gone back in 20 years but I only had one day to do any sightseeing. It’s a fantastic city with a rich culture and heritage so I definitely want to return. The people were a lot trendier than I remember and the traffic was unbelievable, like nothing I’d ever seen before, but I enjoyed it more than my first visit.
